caption.p: CET inhibited ZIKV infection. The inhibition of CET in ZIKV-infected Vero cells was determined by IFA (A). Quantification of Vero cells (B) and A549 cells (C). The data shown here represent the mean and SD of triplicate experiments. Statistical significance was determined via a t-test compared with the ZIKV group: * indicates p < 0.05; ** indicates p < 0.01; and *** indicates p < 0.001.
